data.text:
Office Space In The One Canada Square

One Canada Square stands as the most impressive building in the financial district of Canary Wharf. The building is also named as the second tallest building in the UK, standing at an incredible 236 metres high and consisting of 50 stories. These 50 floors are the UK base to many of the leading businesses across the world. As well as office space, the building benefits from the amenities offered by a large shopping centre which sits below the main towers.
